Instructions: 
 When started up: 
  - LED's will flash, pick one of the following:
    - Red for easy
    - Yellow for hard
    - Green for extreme
    - Blue for multiplayer (4 players)
When pressed, game will start
    - Follow the pattern by pressing the 
      correct buttons to win
Can you beat Simon? Good luck!
